<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased API Error Rates and Launch Failures>
Between 9:28 AM and 12:52 PM PDT we experienced increased API error rates and launch failures in a single Availability Zone in the US-EAST-1 Region. Existing instances were not affected. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
